data.description: Enjoy the coastal lifestyle minutes from the beach and close to shopping, restaurants, entertainment, schools, trails, parks, colleges, and easy access to highways 76,78, and I-5.   This 3BR /2BA single story home in the Alta Vistas community has been updated with; paint, flooring, light fixtures, toilets, mirrors, kitchen appliances, landscaping and more. The home has a bonus large sunroom on a large .18 acres lot with room for back-yard entertaining with NO HOA. Exterior paint and windows are approximately 7 years old. Solar system and HERO loan attached to taxes will be paid off at closing.
